     79          /*******************************************************************************
     80          * Function Name  : WDG_CntOnOffConfig
     81          * Description    : Starts or stops the free auto-reload timer to count down.
     82          * Input          : - NewState: specifies how the timer have to be started 
     83          *                    or stopped. It can be:
     84          *                     ENABLE: the counter loads the Timer pre-load value and
     85          *                     starts counting.
     86          *                     DISABLE: the counter is stopped.
     87          * Output         : None.
     88          * Return         : None.
     89          *******************************************************************************/

